beer.beer_description: Its been a few years since we got together with our old friends & Neighbours in @hopnationbeer to throw down a beer. So a few months back, over a few beers we got talking and came up with the idea of brewing a 2 part IPA series. The beers would use the same Hops, Similar yeast strains/process' but us at Banks brewing a NW Style West Coast IPA showcasing a more malt driven backbone & chewy, resiny character. @hopnationbeer would do the same but in a Cali Style West Coast IPA. showcasing bright punchy Citrus character. With both beers showcasing some of our favourite & epic hops in Nelson Sauvin, Simcoe & Citra. ⁠
